snippet.title: Kura5 Bonds of the Undying - Chapter 2 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Reuploaded from the old channel

What's new?
-New Immortal dungeon (more story)
-Block puzzles...
-New Undead "Hub" dungeon area
-San Miguel expansions
-Locke and Mac's sidequests
-Updated music + new tracks
-Updated Annie's portrait 
-Overhauled input system
-Put Vorn Buddy through intense training
-Gameplay tweaks to Dark Loans, combat, petting Annie's summons, etc
-New items/weapons/summons
-Updated Lunar Knights Nightmare Difficulty password reward
